Package profile

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FriendsListObserver
    Observer in ObserverPattern for updating view whenever friends list updates
    NewsFeedObserver
    ObserverPattern used to notify observers when their subject's news feed changes
    PictureObserver
    ObserverPatter used for updating interested observers when the subject's picture changes
    WallObserver
    ObserverPattern has implementing classes be notified by subject when wall changes
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountModel
    Model class for MVC holding the state of a Facebook account and various methods for its manipulation
    BasicProfileController<T extends BasicProfileView>
    BasicProfileController acts as Controller for Facebook MVC Pairs with BasicProfileView to display only name, picture, search bar, settings, and logout Meant to be extended for further functionality
    BasicProfileView
    The most basic profile view for facebook project Displays only name, profile picture, search bar, settings, and logout
    FacebookDatabase
    Class for holding overall collection of LoginModels and paired AccountModels Extension of HashMap for implementation of JSON-related methods specific to this project
    FriendProfileController
    Extension of BasicProfileController for controlling display of friend's wall and unfollow button
    FriendProfileView
    Extension of BasicProfileView for displaying friend's wall and unfollow button
    NewsFeedModel
    Class representing the news feed of a facebook profile Holds the posts of other people and keeps track of who authored each
    OwnProfileController
    Extends BasicProfileController to include wall, news feed, and friends list myAcc_model is also used as dispAcc_model
    OwnProfileTestDriver  
    OwnProfileView
    Extends BasicProfileView to include wall, news feed, friends list, and ability to post as a friend
    StrangerProfileController
    Extends BasicProfileController to add a button for following (becoming friends)
    StrangerProfileView
    Extends BasicProfileView to display a follow button
